> Hello,
>
> I can hear a leak in the manifold near the air intake, but does not seem
to
> be coming from the gasket.  It seem to be coming from the manifold - See
> Picures: http://filebox.vt_dot_edu/users/sselin/pics/vaccum_leak.htm
>
> I used a tube as a stethescope and am pretty sure that's where I am
hearing
> the leak.  Anyone have experience with this.</pre>


